column2: SELECT   d.RAJ2# AS input_ra, d.DEJ2# AS input_dec, s.ra as s_ra, s.dec as s_dec, s.z as s_z,   s.specObjID as s_specObjID, e.specObjID as e_specObjID, s.sciencePrimary, m.* into mydb.MyTable_# from MyDB.CAGN_QSO2_radec AS d     OUTER APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjEq( d.RAJ2#, d.DEJ2#, #) AS n      LEFT JOIN SpecObjAll AS s ON n.objid=s.bestObjID      LEFT JOIN emissionLinesPort AS e ON s.specObjID=e.specObjID      LEFT JOIN stellarMassStarFormingPort AS m ON m.specObjID=s.specObjID
